metadata.name: THEOHTANIS #1
metadata.description: Theohtanis PFP 10,000 Collection is an epic story telling expression of art imitating unimaginable talent in reality through an artist representation of Shohei Ohtani (大谷翔平) AKA (にとうりゅうthat literally means “two-sword style”, Nitoryu/Nitōryū) There will be two anime types Samurai's and the Urban Inspired Over Seas OG's . TheOhtanis utility is two fold Long term community building in IRL and the Metaverse. Merging IRL collecting, web3 collecting and Gaming. TheOhtanis Holders will be able to participate in Future Holder Exclusive Investment Grade Vaulted Physical Backed Asset NFT Drops. The 1st of many different PNFT Drops will be TheOhtanis 1000+ Graded Rookie Card Drop Date TBD. Slablox.io is the web3 Dev Team.
